{
  "texts": [
    "The proposed VMD-CNN and IF-CNN models, followed by TVF-CNN, WPD-CNN, and CEEMDAN-CNN models achieve the best forecasting precision in all studied regions.",
    "The VMD-CNN and IF-CNN models provide the highest average PV power production, which will be evaluated as the best candidate algorithm for multiscale fusing.",
    "For a more comprehensive view of the model's precision, a statistical representation is also required in order to have a better comprehension of model precision.",
    "As shown in Fig. 4, the VMD-CNN model ranked as the best forecasting model for Laghouat and Sidi bel abbes PV station followed by the IF-CNN model.",
    "In the case of Ghardaia PV station, we observe that the IF-CNN model provides the best forecasting performance followed by the VMD-CNN model."
  ]
}